<p><strong>Sheet 2: ROI Calculation</strong></p>
<p>For each month, calculate:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Total revenue</strong> = (Organic conversions + AI referral conversions) x Average conversion value</li>
<li><strong>Total cost</strong> = Software + Labor + Content production</li>
<li><strong>Net return</strong> = Total revenue - Total cost</li>
<li><strong>ROI %</strong> = (Net return / Total cost) x 100</li>
<li><strong>Cumulative ROI</strong> = (Cumulative net return / Cumulative total cost) x 100</li>
</ol>
<p>Add a row for <strong>time savings value</strong> = Hours saved x Loaded hourly rate. This is a cost reduction, so add it to your net return.</p>
